    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Ninjutsu (Raiton)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 2 (Spell Level 1)</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 4</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 14 | <b>Successes:</b> 1</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 2 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 13</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> S</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>You charge your hands with crackling electricity, dealing 2d6 electric damage, +1 per level (up to 2d6+5 total) against the target on hit. If the target wears a lot of metal (such as metal armor), you gain a +2 bonus to the attack roll (GM's discretion).</p>\n\n\n\n",
